# Editing rules wrapper

This file is a Cursor wrapper. Canonical editing and workflow rules live in:

- [docs/ai/AGENT_RULES.md](../../docs/ai/AGENT_RULES.md)
- [PHILOSOPHY.md](../../PHILOSOPHY.md)

Operational highlights:

- Do not write custom macro event loops.
- Keep Maker lifecycle and histogram management in `StMaker` code.
- Prefer YAML edits over recompilation when changing thresholds and cuts.
- Keep `analysis_info` and mainconf-linked metadata synchronized.
- If scripts or run flow change, update REFERENCE/INSTALL/README/job-run docs.
